{
  "texts": [
    "Obtaining their preferences comprehensively is especially important.",
    "In the current big data environment, the use of intelligent algorithms to construct a model for discovering key design features of products, considering the issues of the priority of design features, design costs, and efficiency, can help designers focus on key design parameters and information during the design process.",
    "On the basis of their close relationship with product functionality and consumer satisfaction, designers can quickly obtain design solutions.",
    "In a previous study, a method for AI-generated review detection and consumer preference analysis was proposed and experimentally validated.",
    "In this section, the experimental results are compared with those of other existing methods."
  ]
}